import React from 'react';
import { Col, Row } from 'react-bootstrap';

const Myposts = () =>{
    return(
        <Col xs='12'>
            <Row>
                <Col xs='12'>
                    <textarea name="" id="" cols="30" rows="10"></textarea>
                    <button></button>
                </Col>
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <Col xs='12'>Post 1</Col>
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <Col xs='12'>Post 2</Col>
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <Col xs='12'>Post 3</Col>
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <Col xs='12'>Post 4</Col>
            </Row>
        </Col>
    );
}
export default Myposts;
